import React from 'react'
import {ChakraProvider, Container, Box, Stack, Text, Heading, Center} from '@chakra-ui/react'

const Header = () => {
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Container>
                <Center>
                <Stack direction="row" spacing="400px">
                    <Box>
                        <Text fontSize="19px" fontWeight="800">Home</Text>
                    </Box>
                    <Box w="23px" h="23px" mt={10} bg="tomato">ss</Box>
                </Stack>
                </Center>
            </Container>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}


export default Header
